title: Total population of Myanmar 2024
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Inhabitants in millions. In total the number of data points it has is 11.
Overall Inhabitants in millions has increased over the Year.
Inhabitants in millions is slightly increasing from 2014 to 2017, roughly constant from 2017 to 2019, and lastly slightly increasing from 2019 to 2024.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum Inhabitants in millions, about 54.65 was reported at Year 2024
Minimum Inhabitants in millions about 51.42 was reached at Year 2014
